{"tid":750135,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"古天樂電影院將重映《柔道龍虎榜》","createTime":"2018-07-20T15:30:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-22T06:32:19.000Z","uid":38601,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"65c7f6d9dcaec913c96c94ceaff8aa61eddc81e2","tid":750135,"uid":38601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T15:30:35.000Z","msg":"「古天樂電影院louis Koo cinema」命名儀式今晚喺灣仔藝術中心舉行，電影院前身為agn&egrave;s b.電影院，但贊助期完結後，由古天樂投資電影公司天下一同藝術中心合作，舉辦香港好電影放映活動，<span style=\"color: red;\">為期三年，戲院可以容納119人，票價75元，會播放由新晉導演拍攝電影、香港人期待電影、甚至重播受歡迎電影等，首個項目就係電影《逆流大叔》，接住有舊片《柔道龍虎榜》及新片《翠絲》</span>。<br />\n<br />\n古仔中午出席另一活動時已經預告，晚上要開工缺席命名儀式，雖然人唔在但心在，現場播出古仔預先拍攝支持短片，希望呢次合作可以推動香港電影業及幫助新晉導演。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新聞轉載 / 蘋果日報 <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180719/58462842\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180719%2F58462842&d=lNOFKpRqpTM1Ydg%2BMRg%2B6bZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=391dd684\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180719%2F58462842&h=3a410d65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20180719/58462842</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港人經常話香港無好嘅港產片睇<br />\n呢間戲院貴精不貴多 專門揀選值得推薦嘅港產片播放<br />\n比觀眾一種感覺 其實唔係無好港產片 只係無人去推而廣之<br />\n黎到呢間戲院就可以睇到優質嘅港產片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n諗起之前外國有間書店一日只售賣一本書 道理不謀而合<br />\n古天樂真係有心人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《逆流大叔》八月檔期<br />\n《柔道龍虎榜》應該緊接《逆流大叔》重映<br />\n間接預告埋黑仔做變性人個套《翠絲》幾個月後上映<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"942f4edfad0177e5755c12e9c92cf7e080cd5933","tid":750135,"uid":42848,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T15:43:26.000Z","msg":"我做姿三四郎，你做檜桓！"},{"pid":"bc3e0b795117fcdb11277f0902cb34e308e1e5cd","tid":750135,"uid":39666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"942f4edfad0177e5755c12e9c92cf7e080cd5933","tid":750135,"uid":42848,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T15:43:26.000Z","msg":"我做姿三四郎，你做檜桓！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T15:52:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f9a2e751c0cb028d733015f26d8ecbf75ffc555","tid":750135,"uid":70013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T17:52:09.000Z","msg":"幾鐘意呢套"},{"pid":"c986b38bd3eaba80e1490d1a69ed3ba14a5c8be7","tid":750135,"uid":57007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T11:25:59.000Z","msg":"原來已經賣緊飛"},{"pid":"0a4f44f6f468a4d1355a7c86ac96c42a4e123aa9","tid":750135,"uid":38601,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c986b38bd3eaba80e1490d1a69ed3ba14a5c8be7","tid":750135,"uid":57007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T11:25:59.000Z","msg":"原來已經賣緊飛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T06:01:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.hkac.org.hk/tc/calendar.php?id=2308&amp;t=u\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkac.org.hk%2Ftc%2Fcalendar.php%3Fid%3D2308%26t%3Du&d=lNOFKpRqpTM1Ydg%2BMRg%2B6bZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=131da6d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkac.org.hk/tc/calendar.php?id=2308&amp;t=u</a><br />\n<br />\n《柔道龍虎榜》於2004年公映，這部向電影大師黑澤明致敬之作，不僅是影迷心目中香港經典電影，更是杜琪峯導演揚言最喜歡的作品。是次數碼修復版獲選為第二十屆烏甸尼遠東電影節閉幕電影，今年四月在意大利作世界首映，經典重現。首次聯合執導《尋秦記》的新晉導演黎震龍，曾在多部杜琪峯電影中擔任副導演，是次特意選映《柔道龍虎榜》，以其面對逆境永不放棄的精神勉己勉人。<br />\n<br />\n《柔道龍虎榜》數碼修復版<br />\n導演: 杜琪峰<br />\n主演: 古天樂、郭富城、應采兒、梁家輝<br />\n香港| 2004 | 95 分鐘 | 粵語對白，中英文字幕 | DCP | 彩色<br />\n<br />\n數碼修復版亞洲首映<br />\n2018烏甸尼遠東電影節 閉幕電影<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">10/8 (五) 7:30pm<br />\n</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tZSGcD85IlA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DtZSGcD85IlA&d=lNOFKpRqpTM1Ydg%2BMRg%2B6bZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=e403778c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=tZSGcD85IlA</a><br />\n<br />\n竟然無留到兩個禮拜晚場比《逆流大叔》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁翠絲可能九月淡季上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"600357eda71687807218e7f5778737c51b3acc56","tid":750135,"uid":171107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T06:02:15.000Z","msg":"呢套極品黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"244f19dc190e7929b4f3187bd1115074f868724e","tid":750135,"uid":35313,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T06:32:19.000Z","msg":"我而家操得好fit  我好有信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}